                    1.3.10 Release Notes
                  -------------------------

This file contains a description of the major changes to ProFTPD for the
1.3.10 release cycle, from the 1.3.10rc1 release to the 1.3.10 maintenance
releases.  More information on these changes can be found in the NEWS and
ChangeLog files.

1.3.10rc1
----------

  + Disable Nagle algorithm for FTP data transfers
  + Implement support for multi-word environment variable values when parsing
    configurations


  + New Modules

      mod_systemd


  + New Directives

      SFTPKeyFingerprints


  + Changed Directives

      ExtendedLog classes+cmds (Issue #1813)

      SQLAuthTypes SSHA, Sodium

      TCPNoDelay (Issue #1957)
